data.description: Welcome to your new turnkey home! Enjoy the South Florida lifestyle in this beautiful and stunning single-story home. This completely remodeled single family, 4 bedroom 2 bath, (GARAGE CONVERTED in to 4th bedroom).Spacious living and dining room, island/bar and plenty of cabinet space, and a large master bedroom. Step outside to the outdoor kitchen to gather for dinner on the grill, or enjoy your morning breakfast  overlooking your canal view. This home is located in an excellent school district, with the beaches as well as great shopping only a short car ride away.The time is now for your South Florida dream home!
